{"tid":566120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲少女頸纏索帶後腦有傷　伏屍將軍澳住所","createTime":"2018-02-19T15:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T01:11:31.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"e06cc179e30733c7e5e3a9ef7a7910f9b2024fed","tid":566120,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"【23:40更新】少女母親情緒激動，報稱不適，需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n【23:15更新】據悉，死者為21歲姓張少女，上址單位為兩母女居住，晚上8時許，母親返家時發現鐵閘沒有上鎖，但木門關上，覺得有可疑，開門入內時赫見女兒倒卧客廳，頸纏索帶，面部發黑，頸及後腦均有傷口，屋內多處亦怖滿血迹，警方調查後認為事件有可疑，交予將軍澳警區重案組調查，正循謀殺案方向調查。<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時許，一名20多歲少女被發現昏迷在將軍澳廣明苑一單位內，警方接報到場證實少女傷重不治，初步發現死者後腦有傷口，認為事件有可疑，正調查事件原因。大批探員到場調查，氣氛緊張，又在場翻查閉路電視，追查綫索。"},{"pid":"08f9e317fcaaeb7347150dc351c8f9475536f3e3","tid":566120,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180219/57851708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57851708&d=Ux%2BLYFAShSwRtbfuYHZFA26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=37264ccf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57851708&h=238f1245\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180219/57851708</a>"},{"pid":"a4c37b07322ed90353d01673038594bb32049bbc","tid":566120,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1125885341861da213d9f74d150f152651014a3f","tid":566120,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0747bd0522617fd9ac90527359dcf81af1c4b9f2","tid":566120,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor